      <div class="article-teaser">
        Over the Christmas and New Year period, most of the TfL network is open. However, on Christmas Day there's no service on most transport.
        
      </div>
    
    <div class="on-this-page">
      <p>These services are not running today: the Tube, buses, TfL Rail, London Overground, DLR, Trams, River, Emirates Air Line and National Rail.</p>

<p>Taxi and Private Hire; and Santander Cycles are all running today.</p>

<p>See our <a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/?Input=&amp;lineIds=&amp;dateTypeSelect=Future date&amp;direction=&amp;startDate=2019-12-25T00%3a00%3a00&amp;endDate=2019-12-25T23%3a59%3a59">Status updates map</a> for Tube, Overground, TfL Rail, DLR and tram services for 25 December.</p>

<h2>Dial-a-Ride</h2>

<ul>
	<li>No regular bookings. Dial-a-Ride services are for registered members only</li>
</ul>

<h2>Taxi and Private Hire</h2>

<p>Until 06:00 on Friday 27 December:</p>

<ul>
	<li>Black cabs will charge an extra &pound;4 per journey</li>
	<li>There may be an extra charge for private hire vehicles (including minicabs) - check when you book</li>
</ul>

<h2>Santander Cycles</h2>

<p>Santander Cycles are available on Christmas Day and throughout the rest of December.</p>

<ul>
	<li>Cycle for free this Christmas. Make as many 30-minute journeys as you like within 24 hours free of charge. Use code SCXMAS19</li>
	<li>Check availability of Santander Cycles using the <a href="/modes/cycling/santander-cycles/find-a-docking-station">online docking station map</a></li>
	<li>Download the Santander Cycles app from the <a href="https://itunes.apple.com/gb/app/santander-cycles/id974792287?mt=8">App Store</a> or <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=uk.gov.tfl.cyclehire&amp;hl=en_GB">Google Play</a></li>
</ul>

<h2>Driving</h2>

<ul>
	<li>The <a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/modes/driving/congestion-charge">Congestion Charge</a> and&nbsp;<a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/modes/driving/ultra-low-emission-zone">ULEZ charges</a>&nbsp;do not apply today</li>
	<li>The <a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/modes/driving/low-emission-zone">LEZ</a> applies at all times</li>
	<li>See our <a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/traffic/status/?Input=&amp;lineIds=&amp;dateTypeSelect=Future date&amp;direction=&amp;startDate=2019-12-25T00%3a00%3a00&amp;endDate=2019-12-25T23%3a59%3a59">traffic status updates map</a> for Christmas Day</li>
</ul>
      
           
      
      
        
          
